{"word":"H2245 - חָבַב - châbab - khaw-bab' - Love - அன்பு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>חָבַב"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châbab"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-bab'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Love / அன்பு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிநேகி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Qal) to love fervently, to cherish"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (compare <a href=\"#/H2244 - חָבָא - châbâʼ - khaw-baw'/2244\">H2244</a>, <a href=\"#/H2247 - חָבָה - châbâh - khaw-bah'/2247\">H2247</a>); properly to <i>hide</i> (as in the bosom), that is, to <i>cherish</i> (with affection): - love."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2243 - חֹב - chôb - khobe/2243\">H2243</a>, <a href=\"#/H2245 - חָבַב - châbab - khaw-bab'/2245\">H2245</a>, <a href=\"#/H2246 - חֹבָב - Chôbâb - kho-bawb'/2246\">H2246</a>, <a href=\"#/H3160 - יְחֻבָּה - Yᵉchubbâh - yekh-oob-baw'/3160\">H3160</a>"}]}